# TODO

Notes, bugs, and plans for the qchem6 project. Markdown-enabled so headings fold in VS Code.

## Major features (future)

### Convergence acceleration
- **DIIS singular B** (Shepard & Minkoff 2007 eq 23 ŌĆö linear least squares for a
  better condition number; consider SVD-truncating B); 
- **EDIIS**
### Perturbations 
- OOD architecture for 1st/2nd order 
- demo 1st order with SO-coupling (HF, DHF)
- demo 2nd order with MP2.

### Configuration Interaction
- Full/Truncated/multi-reference; 
- goal is to show the OO design supports it.
- Rank by (1) code complexity here, (2) real-world usefulness.

### Parallel execution
